#### Puzzles

Each stage is made up of levels that we call __puzzles__, which hold individual videos, readings, or questions. Puzzles are indicated as circles with numbers, and are visible: 
- on the main PD page
- on the header in any other puzzle on the same stage
- from the header drop-down in any puzzle
<br/>
The colors of the puzle circle will change based on your progress. 
